<?php
return ['messages'=>['#https://eji.com.hk/portfolio_group/jewellery-exhibitions/'=>'#https://eji.com.hk/portfolio_group/jewellery-exhibitions/','<h4><a href="https://eji.com.hk/the-mastery-behind-our-craft-excellence-in-every-facet-of-our-jewellery-manufacturing/">The Mastery Behind Our Craft: Excellence in Every Facet of Our Jewellery Manufacturing</a></h4>'=>'<h4><a href="https://eji.com.hk/zh-hant/%e7%b2%be%e6%b9%9b%e5%b7%a5%e8%97%9d%ef%bc%9a%e7%8f%a0%e5%af%b6%e8%a3%bd%e9%80%a0%e5%90%84%e5%80%8b%e6%96%b9%e9%9d%a2%e7%9a%84%e5%8d%93%e8%b6%8a%e5%93%81%e8%b3%aa/">精湛工藝：卓越珠寶製作</a></h4>','<h5>June 20, Thursday - June 22, Saturday<br />10am - 6pm</h5><h5>June 23, Sunday<br />10am - 5pm</h5>'=>'<h5>6 月 20 日（週四）至 6 月 22 日（週六）<br>上午 10 點至下午 6 點</h5><h5>6 月 23 日（星期日）<br>上午 10 點至下午 5 點</h5>','<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: Poppins;">Hong Kong, an ever-bustling metropolis, is not just a global business hub; but also a vibrant canvas for cultural and artistic utterances. Have you ever had a chance to explore different places in this city, apart from attending international jewellery fairs and engaging in business appointments? If you are planning a visit to Hong Kong for the <a href="https://eji.com.hk/portfolio/jewellery-gem-fair-asia-2024/">Jewellery and Gem Asia Fair</a> this June, enrich your stay with these spectacular cultural experiences that promise to mesmerize and inspire. From traditional events to modern art, there’s something for every taste.</span></p>'=>'<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: Poppins;">香港是一個日益繁華的大都市，不僅是一個全球商業中心;同時也是文化和藝術話語的生動畫布。除了參加國際珠寶展和商務約會之外，您是否有機會探索這座城市的不同地方？如果您計劃在今年 6 月訪問香港參加 <a href="https://eji.com.hk/portfolio/jewellery-gem-fair-asia-2024/">亞洲珠寶首飾展覽會</a> ，這些壯觀的文化體驗一定會讓您著迷和啟發，從而豐富您的逗留。從傳統活動到現代藝術，總有一款適合各種口味。   </span></p>','<p>Before your hectic schedule for the Jewellery and Gem Asia Fair, kick off your journey with a bang on the stunning marine pyrotechnic displays at Victoria Harbour on June 15, 2024. These will light up the night sky alongside the multimedia show, “A Symphony of Lights”, which features spectacular lights and music. The breathtaking views of the skyline and Victoria Harbour are sure to impress. More details can be found on the <a href="https://www.discoverhongkong.com/eng/what-s-new/harbour-nightscape-spectacle.html">Hong Kong Tourism Board website</a>.</p>'=>'<p>在您繁忙的亞洲珠寶首飾展覽會日程之前，不妨於 2024 年 6 月 15 日在維多利亞港欣賞令人驚歎的海洋煙火表演，開啟您的旅程。這些將與多媒體表演 「A Symphony of Lights」 一起照亮夜空，該表演以壯觀的燈光和音樂為特色。天際線和維多利亞港的壯麗景色一定會給人留下深刻印象。詳情請流覽 <a href="https://www.discoverhongkong.com/eng/what-s-new/harbour-nightscape-spectacle.html">香港旅遊發展局網頁</a>。   </p>','<p>Delve into the multisensory world of floral art blossom at the renowned Naked Flowers Hong Kong Art Exhibition by Japanese artist Ryotaro Muramatsu. This immersive experience offers a unique perspective and inspiration on nature’s aesthetics. Tickets are available for $180 at <a href="https://hk.trip.com/travel-guide/attraction/hong-kong/uob-kayhian-presents-naked-flowers-hong-kong-145018737/?locale=en_hk">Trip.com</a>. Don’t miss this captivating art adventure if you appreciate art and nature.</p>'=>'<p>在著名的 Naked Flowers Hong Kong Art Exhibition 中，深入探索花藝的多感官世界，欣賞由日本藝術家 Ryotaro Muramatsu 創作的藝術盛開。這種身臨其境的體驗為大自然的美學提供了獨特的視角和靈感。門票在 <a href="https://hk.trip.com/travel-guide/attraction/hong-kong/uob-kayhian-presents-naked-flowers-hong-kong-145018737/?locale=en_hk">Trip.com</a> 售價 180 美元。如果您欣賞藝術和自然，千萬不要錯過這個迷人的藝術冒險。   </p>','<p>Experience the charm of old Hong Kong at Lin Heung Lau, a 135-year-old tea house that has recently reopened at its original site on Wellington Street. Known for serving traditional dim sum in an old-fashioned way – with rushed staff pushing trolley carts loaded with bamboo steamers - this is the perfect place to savor the city’s culinary heritage and indulge in a bit of nostalgia. Discover more about this iconic location <a href="https://www.afoodieworld.com/blog/2024/04/03/lin-heung-lau-teahouse-reopens/">here</a>.</p>'=>'<p>在蓮香樓體驗舊香港的魅力，這是一家擁有 135 年歷史的茶館，最近在惠靈頓街的原址重新開業。以老式供應傳統點心而聞名 - 匆忙的工作人員推著裝滿竹蒸籠的手推車 - 這是品嘗這座城市的美食遺產並沉浸在懷舊情懷中的理想場所。 <a href="https://www.afoodieworld.com/blog/2024/04/03/lin-heung-lau-teahouse-reopens/">在此處</a>瞭解有關這個標誌性地點的更多資訊。  </p>','<p>Explore the dynamic world of street art at the HKwalls Street Art Festival, where international and local artists transform the city’s walls to into vibrant, large murals and artworks. This festival is a splendid visual feast that showcases the creative pulse of Hong Kong. Be sure to capture these instagrammable street arts around the town and dive into the colourful vibes at <a href="https://www.hkwalls.org/festivals/hkwalls-2024/">HKwalls 2024</a>!</p>'=>'<p>在 HKwalls Street Art Festival 探索充滿活力的街頭藝術世界，國際和本地藝術家將城市的城牆改造成充滿活力的大型壁畫和藝術品。這個節日是一場精彩的視覺盛宴，展示了香港的創意脈搏。一定要在城裡捕捉這些適合 Instagram 的街頭藝術，並在 <a href="https://www.hkwalls.org/festivals/hkwalls-2024/">HKwalls 2024</a> 上沉浸在多彩的氛圍中！  </p>','<p>Immerse yourself in the competitive spirit and cultural pageantry of the Hong Kong International Dragon Boat Races on June 15 &amp; 16, 2024. Witness thousands of dragon boat athletes from around the world paddling fiercely along the Tsim Sha Tsui East harbourfront. This exhilarating event is a must-see for its vibrant atmosphere and thrilling races in the birthplace of modern dragon boat racing. Learn more about the event <a href="https://www.discoverhongkong.com/eng/what-s-new/events/dhk-highlighted-events/dragon-boat-races.html">here</a>.</p>'=>'<p>沉浸在2024年6月15日和16日舉行的香港國際龍舟賽的競爭精神和文化盛況中。見證來自世界各地的數千名龍舟運動員在尖沙咀東海濱激烈劃槳。這項令人振奮的活動因其充滿活力的氛圍和在現代龍舟比賽的發源地舉行的驚心動魄的比賽而值得一看。 <a href="https://www.discoverhongkong.com/eng/what-s-new/events/dhk-highlighted-events/dragon-boat-races.html">在此處</a>瞭解有關該活動的更多資訊。   </p>','<p>Whether you are an art and cultural enthusiast, spend some time walking through the city. These experiences in Hong Kong will undoubtedly add a memorable richness to your business trip to <a href="https://eji.com.hk/portfolio/jewellery-gem-fair-asia-2024/">Jewellery and Gem Asia Fair</a>. Don’t forget to visit us to explore our fabulous new collections and experience our exceptional bespoke services. It is also a perfect opportunity to share your discoveries and insights from your visits.</p><p>We are confident that the hidden gems of Hong Kong will enrich your experiences in the city like never before. This time, the unique charm and vibrant culture of Hong Kong will surely make you fall in love with this fascinating place!</p>'=>'<p>無論您是藝術和文化愛好者，都可以花一些時間在城市中漫步。這些在香港的體驗無疑會為您的 <a href="https://eji.com.hk/portfolio/jewellery-gem-fair-asia-2024/">Jewellery and Gem Asia Fair</a> 商務旅行增添難忘的豐富性。別忘了訪問我們，探索我們精彩的新系列，體驗我們卓越的定製服務。這也是分享您訪問中的發現和見解的絕佳機會。   </p><p>我們深信，香港隱藏的瑰寶將以前所未有的方式豐富您在這座城市的體驗。這一次，香港獨特的魅力和充滿活力的文化一定會讓您愛上這個迷人的地方！ </p>','Contact Our Sales Experts'=>'聯繫我們的銷售專家','HKwalls Street Art Festival'=>'HKwalls 街頭藝術節','Historic Yumcha at Lin Heung Lau'=>'蓮香樓 （Lin Heung Lau） 的 Historic Yumcha','Hong Kong International Dragon Boat Races'=>'香港國際龍舟賽','More Jewellery Exhibitions'=>'更多珠寶展覽','Naked Flowers Hong Kong Art Exhibition'=>'Naked Flowers 香港藝術展','Opening Hour'=>'上班時間','Photograph: Facebook @Lin Heung Tea House '=>'照片：Facebook @Lin香茶館  ','Photograph: HKwalls'=>'圖片：HKwalls','Photograph: Hong Kong China Dragon Boat Association'=>'圖片：中國香港龍舟總會','Photograph: Hong Kong Tourism Board'=>'照片：香港旅遊發展局','Photograph: Instagram @naked_inc'=>'照片：Instagram @naked_inc','Pyrotechnic Displays'=>'煙火表演','READ MORE'=>'閱讀更多','Register Now'=>'立即註冊','caption-image-28ae7e5'=>'照片：Instagram @naked_inc','caption-image-6f816a9'=>'圖片：中國香港龍舟總會','caption-image-997e63d'=>'照片：香港旅遊發展局','caption-image-9f767e8'=>'圖片：HKwalls','caption-image-a28d2da'=>'照片：Facebook @Lin香茶館  ','editor-text-editor-08d4874'=>'<h5>6 月 20 日（週四）至 6 月 22 日（週六）<br>上午 10 點至下午 6 點</h5><h5>6 月 23 日（星期日）<br>上午 10 點至下午 5 點</h5>','editor-text-editor-691aa82'=>'<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 11.